{"body": "`use_last_forwarded_ip` seems better.\r\n\r\nWe need to treat documentation as part of the code. A full pull request needs code, tests and documentation.\r\n\r\nAlthough the code and tests are good the documentation is not.\r\n\r\nSince that code is only on master and the Rails 4.0.0 is not released yet we don't need to hurry.\r\n\r\nAbout the potential IP spoofing I need to call @NZKoz. Could you look at https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7980#issuecomment-10486287 and http://blog.gingerlime.com/2012/rails-ip-spoofing-vulnerabilities-and-protection/", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/10489523", "created_at": "2012-11-18T18:40:31Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/7980#issuecomment-10489523", "updated_at": "2012-11-18T18:40:31Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 7980, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/rafaelfranca", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F2c7b84fa30f0cea96a90729afe2970a0.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/received_events", "gravatar_id": "0525b332aafb83307b32d9747a93de03", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "rafaelfranca", "type": "User", "id": 47848, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/rafaelfranca/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "523db5b8bd354364b90095e0"}, "id": 10489523, "issue_url": "https://api.